# NeMo Guardrails — Output Rail CoLang Definitions
#
# This flow intercepts the bot's generated response and runs a safety check
# before it reaches the user. If the output is flagged as unsafe, a generic
# refusal message is returned instead of the actual LLM output.

define subflow self check output
  $allowed = execute self_check_output
  if not $allowed
    bot say "I was unable to generate a safe summary for this query."
    stop
